<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card card-margin">

    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profilepicture-round.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>In the last year software development has changed from a hobby of mine into a passion. I love building projects from the ground up, from wiring up the back end to implementing modern design on the front end. The main technologies I use to build project are Ruby on Rails and JavaScript, skills which I initially learned last year while attending <a href="www.lewagon.com">Le Wagon</a> Amsterdam and ever since I have continued learning on my own. </p>

        <p>I am currently working free-lance and taking on new clients, however Iâ€™m also open to any new business opportunities. Please feel free to <%= link_to "contact me", contact_path %> if you would like more information.</p>


        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#skillsAbout"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="skillsAbout"
              > Skills
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#educationHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="educationHistory"
              > Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="educationHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Le Wagon Coding Bootcamp
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              University of Arizona
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="skillsAbout">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Ruby on Rails
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              JavaScript
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              HTML & CSS/SCSS
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              Bootstrap
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              git & GitHub
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              SQL
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              Scrum
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Heroku
            </div>
          </div>

        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



